==English==
===Etymology===
From the Book of Genesis of the [[Bible]], in which Adam and Eve are forbidden from eating the [[fruit]] of the Tree of Knowledge of Good and Evil.

===Noun phrase===
'''forbidden fruit'''
#the fruit mentioned above
#something that one should not take or get involved with, such as an another person's [[spouse]]

